lease let me know, if you could also send me a few links to sites you have helped design and or themes you have built so I can pass them along to my friend (since he is the one who will be paying for this) it would be much appreciated.\r\nThanks,\r\n-Chris'),(1,11,1,'0','Melanie Melonhead'),(1,11,2,'0','melaniewilliams33@yahoo.com'),(1,11,3,'0','I wass wundering if yew coode help mee with my speline. Doo yoo halve a webcite for that??\r\n\r\nThaanctst!');
